1068
01:30:10,150 --> 01:30:11,520
Song Seo-rae, listen carefully.

1069
01:30:13,180 --> 01:30:14,380
An alibi this time,

1070
01:30:16,050 --> 01:30:17,770
it must be hard, like the rock under our feet!

1071
01:30:23,150 --> 01:30:24,720
Do you think your wife is the killer?

1072
01:30:25,220 --> 01:30:26,220
How come?

1073
01:30:26,490 --> 01:30:28,110
Because there is no sign of invasion, no sign of theft,

1074
01:30:28,130 --> 01:30:29,200
