1075
01:30:29,960 --> 01:30:32,140
Because of the stabs in the chest?

1076
01:30:32,460 --> 01:30:34,960
Do you think this is a revenge murder?

1077
01:30:35,890 --> 01:30:38,080
Or maybe because his wife wasn't shocked or sad?

1078
01:30:39,510 --> 01:30:42,070
It varies from person to person, some people grieve, others are colder.

1079
01:30:43,620 --> 01:30:45,690
