1080
01:30:45,890 --> 01:30:47,610
Why don't you do it to others too?

1081
01:30:52,330 --> 01:30:54,720
I met her in Busan last year, in the case of the mountain accident,

1082
01:30:56,050 --> 01:30:57,530
