1083
01:30:57,920 --> 01:30:59,030
Did she kill him?

1084
01:31:01,200 --> 01:31:04,960
I wondered if she could be the killer.

1085
01:31:05,330 --> 01:31:06,850
That case was classified as a suicide.

1086
01:31:07,120 --> 01:31:09,880
And now, her new husband is dead here, and still under my jurisdiction.

1087
01:31:10,490 --> 01:31:11,670
But she is right-handed.

1088
01:31:12,910 --> 01:31:14,370
So think about it!

1089
01:31:14,390 --> 01:31:16,060
How could she be a criminal?

1090
01:31:21,560 --> 01:31:23,120
They want me to go to the police station

1091
01:31:24,000 --> 01:31:25,670
Can i take my handbag?

1092
01:31:28,820 --> 01:31:30,130
You went for a walk.

1093
01:31:31,520 --> 01:31:34,150
And you didn't have a cell phone with you, so there's no way to track your location.

1094
01:31:34,170 --> 01:31:35,680
Can you prove your alibi?

1095
01:31:36,580 --> 01:31:37,580
I know it.

1096
01:31:39,690 --> 01:31:41,200
You don't seem to be worried.

1097
01:31:43,150 --> 01:31:45,400
Did your husband have enemies?

1098
01:31:46,960 --> 01:31:48,150
I read that he borrowed some money,

1099
01:31:48,170 --> 01:31:49,970
invested a lot and lost a lot.

1100
01:31:50,080 --> 01:31:52,770
He's been losing a lot of money lately.

1101
01:31:53,090 --> 01:31:55,540
Did you lose money and still live in a luxury villa?

1102
01:31:56,370 --> 01:31:59,010
In order to have money, you need to demonstrate that you have a certain lifestyle.

1103
01:32:02,720 --> 01:32:04,820
Why did you marry such a man?

1104
01:32:07,700 --> 01:32:09,040
I married a man ...

1105
01:32:09,870 --> 01:32:13,880
but I was deciding to leave him.

1106
01:32:21,010 --> 01:32:23,110
Why did you come to Ipo?

1107
01:32:24,930 --> 01:32:26,890
No particular reason.

1108
01:32:27,830 --> 01:32:30,550
If there is one, the creditors will find me.

1109
01:32:42,150 --> 01:32:44,500
You don't marry a man simply because you love him.

1110
01:32:45,460 --> 01:32:47,590
Your husband gets threats.

1111
01:32:48,660 --> 01:32:49,660
And then it dies.

1112
01:32:50,600 --> 01:32:51,840
Like last year.

1113
01:32:52,460 --> 01:32:53,460
What?

1114
01:32:54,890 --> 01:32:56,650
My previous husband committed suicide.

1115
01:32:56,960 --> 01:32:58,680
This husband was murdered.

1116
01:33:02,820 --> 01:33:03,820
Bene.

1117
01:33:06,520 --> 01:33:07,650
Your two husbands,

1118
01:33:08,210 --> 01:33:10,070
in areas very far from each other,

1119
01:33:11,250 --> 01:33:13,360
in remote jurisdictions,

1120
01:33:14,090 --> 01:33:15,720
