1124
01:33:26,560 --> 01:33:28,390
What do you think people would say?

1125
01:33:32,640 --> 01:33:37,300
What a poor woman.

1126
01:34:23,960 --> 01:34:26,580
This was not the dress, it was a blue dress,

1127
01:34:26,950 --> 01:34:27,950
