1158
01:37:34,720 --> 01:37:35,780
Song Seo-rae.

1159
01:37:36,560 --> 01:37:40,730
You just admitted that you took out all the most important evidence of the murder.

1160
01:37:42,400 --> 01:37:44,010
As a suspect in the murder of Lin Ho-shin,

1161
01:37:44,020 --> 01:37:45,940
I'm putting you under arrest now.

1162
01:37:49,080 --> 01:37:52,440
"I don't like the police following my husband."

