1167
01:38:02,490 --> 01:38:03,490
Yes, sir.

1168
01:38:06,550 --> 01:38:08,280
You are a male?

1169
01:38:08,710 --> 01:38:09,710
No.

1170
01:38:10,870 --> 01:38:13,030
Have you ever killed anyone?

1171
01:38:14,230 --> 01:38:15,230
Yup.

1172
01:38:16,970 --> 01:38:20,310
Did you kill your husband, Lin Ho-shin?

1173
01:38:26,770 --> 01:38:27,770
No.

1174
01:38:51,810 --> 01:38:52,810
Gentleman.

1175
01:38:55,720 --> 01:38:56,770
What are you doing here?

1176
01:39:10,480 --> 01:39:12,230
This is the recording extracted from the smartwatch.

1177
01:39:12,750 --> 01:39:17,630
As he asked, we checked the license plates around the mansion before and after the murder.

1178
01:39:18,260 --> 01:39:20,790
Among them is that of a person who was scammed by Lin Ho-shin.

1179
01:39:21,510 --> 01:39:22,980
