1191
01:40:03,290 --> 01:40:05,370
He worked eighteen hours a day.

1192
01:40:05,400 --> 01:40:08,170
I trusted Lin Ho-shin, he was rich, and I gave him all that money.

1193
01:40:08,720 --> 01:40:10,630
In the beginning it was only 10 million Won.

1194
01:40:10,920 --> 01:40:12,560
And he paid the dividends little by little,

1195
01:40:12,590 --> 01:40:15,720
it's always nice to get interest.

1196
01:40:16,350 --> 01:40:18,570
Then he convinced me to give him all the savings.

1197
01:40:18,760 --> 01:40:20,780
But then I knew he was going to all places,

1198
01:40:21,030 --> 01:40:22,550
where you gamble,

1199
01:40:22,650 --> 01:40:24,530
