1200
01:40:24,650 --> 01:40:26,650
He spent my money like a pig, that son of a bitch!

1201
01:40:27,840 --> 01:40:28,880
In all, he had raised 10 billion Won.

1202
01:40:30,780 --> 01:40:32,770
My mother had severe diabetes.

1203
01:40:33,530 --> 01:40:35,190
And he also had a nervous breakdown,

1204
01:40:35,210 --> 01:40:36,610
after learning that the money was gone.

1205
01:40:36,630 --> 01:40:38,330
Kidney complications have also arisen.

1206
01:40:39,120 --> 01:40:40,840
Because he didn't get the proper treatment!

1207
01:40:40,920 --> 01:40:43,200
They had to amputate her ten toes !.

1208
01:40:43,890 --> 01:40:46,090
Do you know why my nickname is "Wa-Sung"? . "(NdT: Iron stone)"

1209
01:40:46,900 --> 01:40:49,030
Because I'm good at slapping people with this iron hand.

1210
01:40:49,030 --> 01:40:50,390
That's why they call me "Wa-Sung".

1211
01:40:50,550 --> 01:40:53,820
Because I don't hit with fists, but with slaps.

1212
01:40:54,050 --> 01:40:55,500
Slaps can be given many and they hurt more than punches.

1213
01:40:56,610 --> 01:40:57,900
But I...

1214
01:40:58,180 --> 01:40:59,830
I didn't kill Ho-shin.

1215
01:40:59,980 --> 01:41:01,250
That beast!

1216
01:41:01,440 --> 01:41:02,830
You know Song Seo-Rae.

1217
01:41:03,850 --> 01:41:05,950
Did you ask Song Seo-Rae to kill her husband?

1218
01:41:07,960 --> 01:41:09,740
Actually I ...

1219
01:41:10,590 --> 01:41:13,520
I'm not the kind of person who can tell others what to do.

1220
01:41:13,920 --> 01:41:15,810
Song Seo-Rae, it really helped me.

1221
01:41:16,250 --> 01:41:17,920
But he will never know,

1222
01:41:18,180 --> 01:41:20,010
who cannot escape from me,

1223
01:41:20,250 --> 01:41:21,970
No matter how many times he tries!

1224
01:41:26,670 --> 01:41:29,260
I have installed tracking software

1225
01:41:31,240 --> 01:41:32,910
