1240
01:42:18,760 --> 01:42:19,820
That's what I thought.

1241
01:42:21,020 --> 01:42:22,770
The turtle thief is on the run on a motorcycle,

1242
01:42:22,790 --> 01:42:24,700
direction Greenstone Walls, third intersection from the sea.

1243
01:42:25,120 --> 01:42:27,280
I repeat! Greenstone Walls, third intersection from the sea.

1244
01:42:40,970 --> 01:42:43,950
Hey, alright. Stand still!

1245
01:42:44,710 --> 01:42:45,710
Let's gather the turtles!

1246
01:42:49,490 --> 01:42:50,590
Hurry!

1247
01:42:51,170 --> 01:42:52,170
You on your feet!

1248
01:42:52,200 --> 01:42:53,680
Load it on your back, we have to take it away.

1249
01:42:53,690 --> 01:42:54,170
Yes, sir.

1250
01:42:54,450 --> 01:42:56,260
Hey, hey. Jump on my back!

1251
01:42:56,850 --> 01:42:57,760
Let's get the big ones first.

1252
01:42:57,790 --> 01:42:59,230
Watch out for your fingers! They bite!

1253
01:43:16,840 --> 01:43:18,240
We caught the turtle thief.

1254
01:43:22,610 --> 01:43:25,720
The husband of a woman I have known,

1255
01:43:25,990 --> 01:43:27,970
