1257
01:43:31,720 --> 01:43:33,160
A man met by chance.

1258
01:43:34,800 --> 01:43:37,500
Wrong number?

1259
01:43:39,560 --> 01:43:41,520
I might as well think this.

1260
01:43:42,550 --> 01:43:45,300
But what if that man is killed after a few days?

1261
01:43:46,480 --> 01:43:47,480
Tesoro.

1262
01:43:55,030 --> 01:43:56,330
Did you kill him?

1263
01:44:04,960 --> 01:44:06,400
Did you and his wife kill him together?

1264
01:44:08,980 --> 01:44:10,200
How are the fingers?

1265
01:44:12,130 --> 01:44:13,970
This is the number of another cell phone Lin Ho-shin used.

1266
01:44:14,330 --> 01:44:15,720
Monitor where he was before he was killed.

1267
01:44:18,380 --> 01:44:21,930
"Take the opportunity! Open up to a new world!"

1268
01:44:23,290 --> 01:44:24,290
Gentleman.

1269
01:44:24,810 --> 01:44:25,810
Yup?

1270
01:44:31,440 --> 01:44:34,620
Why was the phone here when the owner died at home?

1271
01:44:34,870 --> 01:44:36,230
Here the owner's phone turns on and off.

1272
01:44:37,760 --> 01:44:38,980
Put your arm one more time,

1273
01:44:39,000 --> 01:44:40,360
