1274
01:44:41,340 --> 01:44:43,010
Oh, my arm hurts.

1275
01:44:47,040 --> 01:44:48,040
Stop like this!

1276
01:44:52,480 --> 01:44:53,860
He was throwing away the phone!

1277
01:44:54,180 --> 01:44:56,180
Call the divers and let's start looking in the area.

1278
01:44:56,380 --> 01:44:57,380
Does it have to be under there?

1279
01:44:57,840 --> 01:44:59,330
One moment, one moment!

1280
01:44:59,730 --> 01:45:01,250
We have already caught the criminal!

1281
01:45:01,550 --> 01:45:03,220
There is evidence and we have a confession!

1282
01:45:03,940 --> 01:45:06,270
Please, stop being obsessed with your wife.

1283
01:45:06,900 --> 01:45:08,300
Doesn't he have pity on her?

1284
01:45:27,040 --> 01:45:28,720
"Are you wearing shoes?"

1285
01:45:29,220 --> 01:45:30,160
"I can see his beard."

1286
01:45:30,190 --> 01:45:32,580
" He's lazy to shave,"

1287
01:45:32,970 --> 01:45:33,970
"in the morning and in the evening?"

1288
01:45:36,330 --> 01:45:39,380
"He seems devoid of energy ... Is it because he didn't see me?"

1289
01:45:47,690 --> 01:45:50,610
"When he made me that strange Chinese food,"

1290
01:45:50,630 --> 01:45:52,280
I smoked next to him,

1291
01:45:53,260 --> 01:45:54,910
